title: Ultra Street Fighter 4
description:
The greatest game in the world of hand-fight to a new level: Meet the Ultra Street Fighter IV! The new game continues the tradition of the series and includes five new characters and six new levels for the crazy fights. We tweaked gameplay, and yet the game can be improved by setting the original modification. As a nice extra, you can get all the costumes from previous submissions to boot! Hurry to play in Ultra!
